{"tid":254061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"返工值得咩","createTime":"2017-05-23T01:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T02:51:10.000Z","uid":50576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf3202611cf61dc2038b79db4039c63ab7af1b7","tid":254061,"uid":50576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"每個人都為社會貢獻青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係社會只係俾返狗都不如嘅待遇我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c516f874c5468a6ecc9ca182a4927c5f3bcde1","tid":254061,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:30:07.000Z","msg":"quit game比較好"},{"pid":"10e2d6ff972a0910104b192a3391d96a4b833446","tid":254061,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個人都為社會貢獻青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係社會只係俾返狗都不如嘅待遇我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都只為自己先番工<br />\n冇一個人係為社會貢獻, 唔出糧比你做唔做<br />\n你咁講同一啲老野口中講既咩後生貢獻社會<br />\n<br />\n問題只係待遇果度"},{"pid":"e9e290a141da58a40696229f1e9fd1e82a604356","tid":254061,"uid":50576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每個人都為社會貢獻青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係社會只係俾返狗都不如嘅待遇我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都只為自己先番工<br />\n冇一個人係為社會貢獻, 唔出糧比你做唔做<br />\n你咁講同一啲老野口中講既咩後生貢獻社會<br />\n<br />\n問題只係待遇果度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投資人生最寶貴嘅青春（至少我覺得係）<br />\n預期回報低到喊出黎<br />\n<br />\n仲值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a754af1cbb337cf8d1ad09a87d4a5ef6ade5cba7","tid":254061,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每個人都為社會貢獻青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係社會只係俾返狗都不如嘅待遇我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個人都只為自己先番工<br />\n冇一個人係為社會貢獻, 唔出糧比你做唔做<br />\n你咁講同一啲老野口中講既咩後生貢獻社會<br />\n<br />\n問題只係待遇果度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n投資人生最寶貴嘅青春（至少我覺得係）<br />\n預期回報低到喊出黎<br />\n<br />\n仲值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投咩資人生呀又<br />\n回咩報...大把人窮幾世<br />\n同值唔值得有關咩<br />\n講左, 只係為自己先番工<br />\n可以只係為3餐一宿<br />\n可以為做有錢人, 可以屌女<br />\n點解你覺得一定會有條好路比你呢"},{"pid":"13fdb2911d3fda16b80edcf0ee90edaef09f4d7e","tid":254061,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"如果唔計交稅，香港應該得好少人貢獻社會"},{"pid":"f851f51bb360400393aa624c836655ca8c35f199","tid":254061,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"唔係值唔值的問題，係唔番會訓街會餓死的問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除非你的工作就係你的興趣，否則都只係浪費生命去令自己唔餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40e8e763e2e9671b794d04b7e0f19c328666ed0","tid":254061,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:14:27.000Z","msg":"唔值..咪又係要返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4650d02aed03f568e6acf2f0f424191da77c9b6","tid":254061,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}